overview: Lizz fakes an emergency while babysitting which ends her boss's date, but she'll finish it up on her own!  Molly is working for a corrupt politician and she decides to try a little corruption with him herself!  Tanner's a med student who babysits on the side. When her boss comes home injured, she'll put her experience to practice.  Maddy gets locked out of the house while babysitting so she shows the locksmith how grateful she is for his help.  Jada needs some help from her friend who babysits, but the man of the house is the one who really helps her.
title: Babysitter Diaries 8
